# Northwind Analytics

> Northwind Analytics is a privacy-first product analytics platform that helps SaaS teams track activation, retention, and revenue without cookies.

Northwind replaces fragile event pipelines with a single autocapture SDK and a
warehouse-native data model. This file maps the pages most useful for
understanding what Northwind does, how to install it, and how to query data.
Sections are ordered from highest to lowest priority; the Optional section may
be skipped when context is limited.

## Product

- [Overview](https://northwind.com/): what Northwind is, who it is for, and how it differs from cookie-based analytics.
- [Pricing](https://northwind.com/pricing): plans, event quotas, and the free tier limits.
- [Autocapture](https://northwind.com/product/autocapture): how the SDK records events with no manual instrumentation.
- [Warehouse sync](https://northwind.com/product/warehouse): stream raw events into BigQuery, Snowflake, or Postgres.

## Docs

- [Quickstart](https://northwind.com/docs/quickstart): install the SDK and see your first event in under 10 minutes.
- [Installation](https://northwind.com/docs/install): framework guides for React, Next.js, Vue, and plain HTML.
- [Tracking events](https://northwind.com/docs/events): manual events, properties, and naming conventions.
- [Identifying users](https://northwind.com/docs/identify): tie events to accounts and users for retention analysis.
- [Querying data](https://northwind.com/docs/query): the SQL schema and example funnel/retention queries.
- [Data privacy](https://northwind.com/docs/privacy): cookieless design, IP anonymization, and GDPR handling.

## API

- [REST API reference](https://northwind.com/docs/api): endpoints, auth, rate limits, and pagination.
- [SDK reference](https://northwind.com/docs/sdk): every method and configuration option for the JS SDK.

## Guides

- [Build an activation funnel](https://northwind.com/guides/activation): define steps and measure drop-off.
- [Measure retention](https://northwind.com/guides/retention): cohort retention curves from raw events.
- [Self-hosting](https://northwind.com/guides/self-host): run Northwind on your own infrastructure with Docker.

## Company

- [About](https://northwind.com/about): team, mission, and the privacy-first thesis.
- [Contact & support](https://northwind.com/contact): how to reach sales and support.

## Optional

- [Blog](https://northwind.com/blog): product updates and analytics engineering articles.
- [Changelog](https://northwind.com/changelog): release notes for the SDK and dashboard.
- [Security & compliance](https://northwind.com/security): SOC 2, data residency, and subprocessors.
- [Status](https://status.northwind.com): live uptime and incident history.
